metadata.title: Disney Silver Master Key with Gem Beads Pewter Key Ring
features: Goofy, Minnie, Mickey, Donald and Daisy on the Teeth of the Key
description: Silver Master Key with Mickey Icon Pewter Key Ring by Monogram International. This highly detailed silver key has four characters on the teeth of the key: Mickey, Donald, Daisy, and Goofy. It can also be converted to be a pendant for a necklace.
